{"tid":499719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聖誕前吹寒風 下周一跌到11°C","createTime":"2017-12-15T06:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T06:50:06.000Z","uid":10958,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c599161aab29221944da2b3e2188cdc9eea90d5d","tid":499719,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:33:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>聖誕前吹寒風 下周一跌到11&deg;C</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/15/3505096/20171215_ccm_01v6_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F12%2F15%2F3505096%2F20171215_ccm_01v6_w.mp4&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=6283eb72\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/12/15/3505096/20171215_ccm_01v6_w.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n天文台指出，一道冷鋒會在今晚抵達廣東沿岸地區，預料明日本港天氣顯著轉涼，與其相關的強烈冬季季候風會在星期日及隨後數天持續影響華南，本港天氣寒冷、乾燥及風勢頗大。天文台亦進一步調低氣溫預測，指出下周一(18日)，市區有機會跌至僅11&deg;C，新界及高地再低幾度，大家出門返工返學，記緊添衣保暖！<br />\n<br />\n至於下周日(24日)平安夜，氣溫有所回升，早上仍然清涼，日間則較為和暖，料可以過個較和暖的聖誕節。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171215/57584072\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57584072&d=O1HfhjmKIZ%2BMAfpPFEUQrFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=4c8c0e2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171215%2F57584072&h=2935d817\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171215/57584072</a>"},{"pid":"3aeb5adfaf1452eeb82bace3fa951735c5f9ad79","tid":499719,"uid":50708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"毒撚都係留喺屋企架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0161415e237227099def03ef5054d15389bd3262","tid":499719,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:35:19.000